item.title: [HBASE-15302] Reenable the other tests disabled by HBASE-14678
item.summary: Reenable the other tests disabled by HBASE-14678

status.description: A patch for this issue has been uploaded to JIRA by a contributor.

comments.comment: Submit a patch. Change some cases on Put.add -> Put.addColumn. And change WALSplitter.getRegionSplitEditsPath's args from "FileStatus fileBeingSplit" to "String fileNameBeingSplit" since we need only the file name here and it is convenience for test.

fileBeingSplit used to be isCreate, and after HBASE-14949 we remove it since we always pass true.
Do we pass false in some tests here?
I find no test set it to false, and I use a temp file name to be fileNameBeingSplit. The tests can pass locally.
